  "texts": [
    "Moreover, the data set offers two official test-train splits, each dividing the data into 1200 training instances and 600 test instances.",
    "From now on, these splits will be referred to as S1 and S2.",
    "Statistical insights into the data set are presented in Table 1.",
    "This figure presents an overview of the relative distribution of the number of teeth per case in the entire data set, as well as the number of cases that have an artificial socket.",
    "In S1, given that the maxillary and mandibular data points are distinct entities within the data set, there are instances where a patient's maxilla is present in the training split while their mandible is in the test split (or vice versa)."
  ]
}